05:03.470 --> 05:06.394
<i>How's my beautiful godson?</i>

05:06.473 --> 05:08.976
<i>Yes.</i>

05:09.059 --> 05:10.982
Come here.

05:11.061 --> 05:13.905
Hi, sweet pie.

05:13.980 --> 05:16.233
